            "Stops iteration immediately on modification",
            "Used in collections like ArrayList, HashMap",
            "Ensures data consistency",
            "Faster and lightweight"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "bullet",
          "heading": "Fail-safe Iterator",
          "items": [
            "Does not throw ConcurrentModificationException",
            "Allows modification during iteration",
            "Works on a copy of the collection",
            "Iteration continues safely",
            "Used in Concurrent collections like ConcurrentHashMap",
            "May not reflect latest changes",
            "Slightly more memory overhead"
          ]
        }
